Any regrets?

76
00:04:48,162 --> 00:04:49,621
No.

77
00:04:50,164 --> 00:04:52,207
All right, Paul.
I'm not asking for a lot here.

78
00:04:52,375 --> 00:04:55,544
Just give me something. Anything.

79
00:04:56,629 --> 00:04:58,505
- Okay.
- Okay.

80
00:05:01,301 --> 00:05:03,093
