Revolutionary War musket.

110
00:06:58,584 --> 00:07:00,919
You know, I'm so glad I picked you
to help me with this.

111
00:07:01,087 --> 00:07:02,087
- Huh?
- Uh-huh.

112
00:07:02,255 --> 00:07:04,089
