So let me handle this from here on out.

119
00:07:23,651 --> 00:07:25,110
Can I help you?

120
00:07:25,278 --> 00:07:28,822
- Yes, I would like to see that ring, please.
- Or not. Whatever.

121
00:07:30,283 --> 00:07:31,950
