214
00:13:07,495 --> 00:13:10,497
Oh, that's pretty nice,
but I'm gonna go with the one I picked first.

215
00:13:10,664 --> 00:13:14,626
Oh, wake up, Chandler.
The one you picked is gone. It's over.

216
00:13:15,419 --> 00:13:16,878
